<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q29_v1" title="Q29_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En un servicio de fotocopias se cobra de manera proporcional a la cantidad de copias realizadas.</p>
    <div>
      <p>Registro de algunos cobros:</p>
      <p>- 10 copias: <m:math><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:math> pesos</p>
      <p>- 20 copias: <m:math><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math> pesos</p>
      <p>- 30 copias: <m:math><m:mn>1350</m:mn></m:math> pesos</p>
      <p>El precio depende proporcionalmente de la cantidad de copias.</p>
    </div>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa el precio, en pesos, por <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> copias?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Como el cobro es proporcional, el precio por copia es constante. Con <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>450</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:math> pesos por copia, para <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> copias el precio es <m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>. Además, verifica los datos: si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math>; si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1350</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>45</m:mn>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión no representa los cobros dados. Por ejemplo, si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4,5</m:mn></m:math> pesos, pero el enunciado indica que 10 copias cuestan <m:math><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:math> pesos.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión no coincide con los valores del registro. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>55</m:mn></m:math> pesos, pero 10 copias cuestan <m:math><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:math> pesos.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión tampoco representa una relación proporcional con los datos dados. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>460</m:mn></m:math> pesos, pero el registro muestra <m:math><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:math> pesos para 10 copias.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la constante de proporcionalidad</strong></p>
            <p>Si el precio es proporcional a la cantidad de copias, entonces existe un valor fijo por cada copia.</p>
            <p>Usando el primer dato:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>450</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Cada copia cuesta 45 pesos.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Escribir la expresión para <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> copias</strong></p>
            <p>Si una copia cuesta 45 pesos, entonces <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> copias cuestan:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Verificar con los otros datos</strong></p>
            <p>Para 20 copias:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Para 30 copias:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1350</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>La expresión coincide con el registro.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas incorrectas</strong></p>
            <p>Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p>Opción B: <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4,5</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Opción C: <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>55</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Opción D: <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>460</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Ninguna de esas expresiones entrega 450 pesos para 10 copias.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correcta para el precio, en pesos, por <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> copias es <m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la A.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>